data.name: Void Cauldron
data.desc: If an "Infernity" monster(s) and/or a Level 8 DARK Dragon Synchro Monster(s) you control would be destroyed by an opponent's card effect, you can banish 1 "Infernity" card from your GY instead. If you have any cards in your hand, send this card to the GY.

card_sets.set_name: Ghosts From the Past: The 2nd Haunting
